{
  "stem": "24615.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went house to house to ask for food so he gave us, so they give us-- they give us onions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They said when you eat the onion, you'll warm up the blood-- they'll warm you up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some give us bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then we went into one farmer and he told us there is a-- a barn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody is occupying the barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We can go in there to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we went into the barn and we went onto the straw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, two Ukrainians, older ones and two young ones with forks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know the long forks?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started yelling Jude, get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, if you don't get out, we'll put the forks through you and they start.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went out and they were standing with the forks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he start yelling in Polish, you know, this boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, he was a refugee from Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, the parents, they run away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he talked good Polish and he said, he started yelling to them, don't kill Moishe, don't kill Moishe, don't kill Moishe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And while he was yelling, and I want to jump on it, but I would jump on the fork.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a knife here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I just slid down, and I got the knife on one Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I forgot-- or I don't know, the blood start running and they start between them talking and arguing, and we run away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We run and then we start walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What I want to tell you is what the mind-- and we didn't even look back if they're running after us or they're not run after us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went into the house and we asked for food and they gave us food, a lady.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
